              {{ lang() === 'id' ? 'Saya adalah seorang pengembang dengan pengalaman mendalam di bidang pengembangan web dan otomasi industri. Berbasis di Indonesia, saya menjembatani kesenjangan antara rekayasa perangkat lunak modern dan proses manufaktur fisik.' : 'I am a developer with deep experience in web development and industrial automation. Based in Indonesia, I bridge the gap between modern software engineering and physical manufacturing processes.' }}
            </p>
            <p>
              {{ lang() === 'id' ? 'Keahlian saya mencakup teknologi seperti React, ASP.NET, Laravel, dan SQL Server untuk web, sekaligus membangun sistem pemantauan mesin, dasbor OEE, dan mengintegrasikan sistem SCADA/MES di lantai pabrik.' : 'My expertise covers technologies like React, ASP.NET, Laravel, and SQL Server for the web, while simultaneously building machine monitoring systems, OEE dashboards, and integrating SCADA/MES systems on the factory floor.' }}
